divs: Sighting DetailsI don't know what this is but I was just visiting the World's Largest Catfish Kidder Dam Wahpeton ND with a plate of brownies and it just showed up on the photo. I did not see this with my own eyes but looks as though whatever it was it was moving very fast.
Summary: Taken in Wahpeton ND 2008, did not see until I got photo developed.
